        text: Enter or copy and paste usernames separated by commas, semicolons, or whitespace. All usernames provided will be added as the selected role. Existing or duplicate usernames will be ignored.
        language: en
    }
)

textMessage CATEGORY_HELP (
    message {
        text: Categories are used for grouping Customers. The Category will be available when you Add, Modify or Search for a Customer. Category can be made Active or Inactive but only active Categories will be shown when adding or modifying a Customer.
        language: en-us
    }
)

